name: Cronus
description: Atlan. Belongs to the middleweight class of dragons. Good attack and defence. Mainly used as a support dragon.
description_schinese: 阿特兰生物。算是龙的中级。袭击功能好，保护功能也好。主要用作支持龙。
description_russian: Cущество Атлан. Относится к среднему классу драконов. Хорош как в нападении, так и в защите. В основном используется как дракон поддержки.
description_brazilian: Criatura Atlan. Pertence à classe média de dragões. É bom tanto no ataque, como na defesa. É usado principalmente como um dragão de suporte.

name: Ray
description: Neil. Excellent agility and speed. Ray belongs to the lightweight class of dragons. Recommended as an airborne fighter of heavyweight dragons for high speed attack.
description_schinese: 纳尔生物。算是龙的轻级。具有很好的速度和机动性。战斗时由于它的西昌身材，它是挺难打中的一口靶子。
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Относится к легкому классу драконов. Обладает превосходной скоростью и маневренностью. В бою он весьма трудная мишень, благодаря тонкому строению своего тела.
description_brazilian: Criatura Neil. Pertence à classe leve de dragões. Tem uma excelente velocidade e manobrabilidade. Em batalha é um alvo muito difícil, graças à estrutura fina do seu corpo.

name: Inara
description: Atlan. Good speed and agility. Effective surprise attacks.
description_schinese: Atlan. Good speed and agility. Effective surprise attacks.
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Отличается хорошей скоростью и изворотливостью, из–за чего в нее весьма сложно попасть.
description_brazilian: Criatura Atlan. Caracteriza-se por uma boa velocidade e desenvoltura, e por isso é um alvo difícil.

name: Toxor
description: Neil. High speed and agility. Toxor uses an unusual method of flying, releasing poisonous gas from the pores of its wings to create a lift.
description_schinese: 纳尔生物。具有很好的速度和机动性。使用特殊的飞行方法。从龙翼上的毛孔中渗出产生举升力的毒气。
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Обладает прекрасной скоростью и маневренностью. Использует необычный способ полета, выпуская из своих пор на крыльях ядовитый газ, создающий подъемную силу.
description_brazilian: Criatura Neil. Ele tem uma excelente velocidade e manobrabilidade. Ele usa um modo de voo incomum, liberando o gás venenoso de seus poros nas asas, que cria força de elevação.

name: Ogre
description: Neil. Ogre belongs to the heavyweight class. It has incredible firepower and armor but slow speed. It can hit the enemy from far distances thanks to its long firing range.
description_schinese: Neil. Ogre belongs to the heavyweight class. It has incredible firepower and armor but slow speed. It can hit the enemy from far distances thanks to its long firing range.
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Относится к тяжелому классу драконов. Благодаря своей силе способен нести на себе четырехпушечную турель, благодаря чему обладает огромной огневой мощью и броней, но медленной скоростью и поворотом.
description_brazilian: Criatura Neil. Pertence à classe pesada de dragões. Graças ao seu poder, é capaz de suportar a torreta de quatro canhões, e por isso tem grande poder de fogo e armadura, mas a velocidade e rotação lentas.

name: Tiamat
description: Atlan. Incredible firepower and health. High speed ensures istant attack. A threatening opponent for any class of dragon.
description_schinese: 阿特兰生物。具有巨大的火力和健康贮存。会背四筒机枪，这使提阿马特对任何龙级作为可怕的敌手。
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Обладает огромной огневой мощью и запасом здоровья. На себе несет четырехствольную турель, что делает Тиамата грозным противником для любого класса драконов.
description_brazilian: Criatura Atlan. Ele tem um enorme poder de fogo e saúde. Em si carrega uma turreta de quatro canhões, que faz Tiamat um oponente formidável para qualquer classe dos dragões.

name: Fury
description: Atlan. Due to it's agility and speed, this dragon is able to attack quickly and unexpectedly.
description_schinese: Atlan. Due to it's agility and speed, this dragon is able to attack quickly and unexpectedly.
description_russian: Существо Атлан.. Благодаря своей маневренности и скорости движений, этот дракон способен атаковать быстро и неожиданно.
description_brazilian: Criatura Atlan. Devido à sua capacidade de manobra e velocidade, este dragão é capaz de atacar inesperadamente e com rapidez.

name: Vampire
description: Neil. It is considered one of the most dangerous creatures. Vampire turns into a swarm of bats when maneuvering.
description_schinese: 纳尔龙。被认为最危险的生物之一。机动时会变成蝙蝠。
description_russian: Дракон Нейл. Считается одним из самых опасных существ. При маневре превращается в летучих мышей.
description_brazilian: Criatura Neil. É considerado uma das criaturas mais perigosas. Manobrando, transforma-se em morcegos

name: Hyperion
description: Atlan. This dragon is a versatile combat unit due to its universal characteristics.
description_schinese: Atlan. This dragon is a versatile combat unit due to its universal characteristics.
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Дракон является универсальной боевой единицей благодаря средним характеристикам.
description_brazilian: Atlan. This dragon is a versatile combat unit due to its universal characteristics.

name: Devil Ray
description: Neil. Lightweight and maneuverable dragon, which has a small stock of health, but high rates of speed. It is a difficult target in combat.
description_schinese: Neil. Lightweight and maneuverable dragon, which has a small stock of health, but high rates of speed. It is a difficult target in combat.
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Легкий и маневренный дракон, обладающий малым запасом здоровья, но высокими показателями скорости. Является сложной мишенью в бою.
description_brazilian: Neil. Lightweight and maneuverable dragon, which has a small stock of health, but high rates of speed. It is a difficult target in combat.

name: Norra
description: Atlan. A support class Dragon. Norra has a good speed and evasion characteristics, also, it has an average amount of health.
description_schinese: Atlan. A support class Dragon. Norra has a good speed and evasion characteristics, also, it has an average amount of health.
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Относиться к классу поддержки. Дракон обладает хорошими показателями скорости и уворота, имеет среднее количество здоровья.
description_brazilian: Atlan. A support class Dragon. Norra has a good speed and evasion characteristics, also, it has an average amount of health.

name: Septicoid
description: Neil. It has high speed and dodge abilities. Due to its unique flying mechanics it is the most maneuverable dragon.
description_schinese: Neil. It has high speed and dodge abilities. Due to its unique flying mechanics it is the most maneuverable dragon.
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Имеет высокие показатели скорости и уворота. Благодаря особенности своего полета является самым маневренным драконом.
description_brazilian: Neil. It has high speed and dodge abilities. Due to its unique flying mechanics it is the most maneuverable dragon.

name: Adamasto
description: Neil. Heavy and clumsy dragon with a huge amount of health. Due to four barrel turret it has enormous firepower.
description_schinese: Neil. Heavy and clumsy dragon with a huge amount of health. Due to four barrel turret it has enormous firepower.
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Тяжелый и неповоротливый дракон, обладающий колоссальным количеством здоровья. Благодаря четырехствольной турели имеет огромную огневую мощь.
description_brazilian: Neil. Heavy and clumsy dragon with a huge amount of health. Due to four barrel turret it has enormous firepower.

name: Marduk
description: Atlan. Dragon has a large stock of health, and a good speed characteristics. Its four barrel turret allows him to inflict great amount of damage.
description_schinese: Atlan. Dragon has a large stock of health, and a good speed characteristics. Its four barrel turret allows him to inflict great amount of damage.
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Дракон обладает большим запасом здоровья и неплохим показателем скорости, а четырехствольная турель позволяет ему наносить огромный урон.
description_brazilian: Atlan. Dragon has a large stock of health, and a good speed characteristics. Its four barrel turret allows him to inflict great amount of damage.

name: Rage
description: Atlan. Sleek and sharp features of the dragon allow him to develop great speed, thus it performs unexpected and rapid attacks, managing to avoid enemy fire.
description_schinese: Atlan. Sleek and sharp features of the dragon allow him to develop great speed, thus it performs unexpected and rapid attacks, managing to avoid enemy fire.
description_russian: Существо Атлан. Обтекаемые и острые черты дракона позволяют ему развивать огромную скорость, благодаря чему он наносит неожиданные и быстрые удары, успевая скрыться от ответного огня противника.
description_brazilian: Atlan. Sleek and sharp features of the dragon allow him to develop great speed, thus it performs unexpected and rapid attacks, managing to avoid enemy fire.

name: Samedi
description: Neil. It is considered one of the most dangerous creatures because of their variability and fair amount of health.
description_schinese: Neil. It is considered one of the most dangerous creatures because of their variability and fair amount of health.
description_russian: Существо Нейл. Считается одним из самых опасных существ из-за своей переменчивости и высокого показателя здоровья.
description_brazilian: Neil. It is considered one of the most dangerous creatures because of their variability and fair amount of health.

name: Plasma
description: Plasma. Default ammunition for the turret. Turret fires a blast of hot plasma, which burns through the enemy armor.
description_schinese: 机枪的标准弹药。发射时放出烧红的等离子电荷，其使敌人的装甲烧穿。
description_russian: Плазма. Стандартный боезапас турели. При выстреле выпускается заряд раскаленной плазмы, которая прожигает броню противника.
description_brazilian: Plasma. Munição padrão da turreta. A turreta atira uma explosão de plasma quente, que perfura a armadura do inimigo.

name: Rocket
description: Rocket. It has good lethal force. Each rocket is equipped with IFF system. It detonates only when enemy dragons are near.
description_schinese: 每枚导弹设有识别系统。只要敌人来到它的激活地区，导弹才能爆炸。
description_russian: Ракета. Обладает хорошей поражающей силой. Каждая ракета оснащена системой распознавания. Детонация произойдет лишь при попадании в поле ее активации врага
description_brazilian: Foguete. Tem uma força letal. Cada foguete vem com um sistema de Indentificação de alidados ou inimigos. Ele detona quando dragões inimigos estão próximos

name: Plasmaball
description: Plasmaball. Has a higher range and causes more damage than a regular plasma.
description_schinese: 这种武器的作战半径很大，其使敌人遭受的损失也很大
description_russian: Плазмошар. Вооружение отличается обширным радиусом действия и большим уроном
description_brazilian: Bola de plasma. Tem um raio maior e causa mais dano que o regular plasma.

name: Railgun
description: Railgun. It is a power beam that causes a high damage.
description_schinese: 这是电的射线，其使敌人遭受损失
description_russian: Рельса. Представляет собой электрический луч, обладающий большим уроном
description_brazilian: Escopeta Eletromagnética. Um raio poderoso que causa alto dano

description: Stamina kit. Instantly restores stamina, used on accelerated flight, when activated.
description_schinese: 在战斗中激活时，马上恢复加速时费的龙力气
description_russian: Стимулятор. При активации в бою моментально восстанавливает затраченные при ускорении силы дракона
description_brazilian: Kit de energia. Instantaniamente recupera a energia quando ativado, usado no combate acelerado

name: Cooling kit
description: Cooling kit. Instantly cools the turret when activated.
description_schinese: 在战斗中激活时，马上使机枪放冷
description_russian: Охлаждающий набор. При активации в бою моментально охлаждает турель
description_brazilian: Kit de resfriamento. Instantâniamente resfria a turreta quando ativado

name: Mine
description: Mine. Each mine is equipped with IFF system. It detonates only when enemy dragons are near.
description_schinese: 每颗地雷设有识别系统。只要敌人来到它的激活地区，地雷才能爆炸。它也是从敌人隐藏起来的一个好功能。
description_russian: Мина. Каждая мина оснащена системой распознавания. Детонация произойдет лишь при попадании в поле ее активации врага.
description_brazilian: Mina explosiva. Cada mina vem com um sistema de Indentificação de alidados ou inimigos. Ele detona quando dragões inimigos estão próximos

name: Smokescreen
description: Smokescreen. It is an excellent way of escape from the enemy
description_schinese: 具有很好的杀伤能力。
description_russian: Дымовая завеса. Является прекрасным средством скрыться от противника
description_brazilian: Cortina de fumaça. Uma maneira excelente de escapar do inimigo

description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Кронус
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Cronus

name: Hot metal
description:
A skin for Cronus
The dragon’s scales were colored red-hot by hundreds of rocket explosions and the time spent under enemy fire.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
由于在敌人的炮火之下度过漫长时光，并且经历了成百上千次导弹的爆炸伤害，使得龙的鳞片被浸染成灼烧般的炽红色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Время, проведенное в боях, среди вражьего огня и взрывов сотни ракет, раскалило докрасна чешую дракона.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
As escamas deste dragão foram coloridas Vermelho-Fogo pela esplosão de vários foguetes e exposição ao fogo inimigo.

name: Verdigri
description:
A skin for Cronus
In the jungle and dark thickets of forests, in heavy battles under the canopy of the trees, Cronus got a greenish tint to its scales that helps to hide from enemies.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
克罗努斯在森林的草丛、黑暗的灌木丛和树冠下经历了激烈的战斗，得到了可以在敌人眼皮底下隐蔽和藏匿的绿色鳞片。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Среди Джунглей и темных зарослей леса, в тяжелых битвах под кронами древ, кронус приобрел зеленоватый оттенок чешуи, помогающий скрываться от врагов.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
Na mata e nas negras densas florestas, nas duras batalhas debaixo do panorâma de arvores, Cronus adquiriu uma escama esverdeada que o ajuda a se camuflar dos inimigos.

name: Moon flame
description:
A skin for Cronus
Long battles in the area of copper mines gave the scales a deep blue color, and dynamic overload added an elegant white coating.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
在矿区中经历了长时间的战斗，鳞片被镀上深蓝，并且由于动力过载，使得鳞片被添染了典雅的白色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Продолжительные битвы в районе медных рудников придали чешуе глубокий синий цвет, а динамические перегрузки - элегантный белый налет.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
Longas Batalhas na área das minas de cobre deram as escamas um azul profundo em uma dinâmica sobregarga sobre uma cobertura elegante de branco.

name: Frost
description:
A skin for Cronus
Intolerable overloads in the cold and dark skies of Ahros left their frosty mark on the dragon's body.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
在Ahros冰冷又黑暗的天空中进行超过身体负荷的运载，使龙的身体布满了冰霜。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Невыносимые перегрузки в холодных и темных небесах Ахроса оставили свой морозный след на теле дракона.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
Intolerável exesso no frio e nos céus negros de Ahros deixou uma marca gelada no corpo do dragão.

name: Autumn
description:
A skin for Cronus
The dragon's scales have been transformed by its absorption of all autumn colors, reflecting the flames of falling leaves on the dragon's body.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
龙的鳞片缘于秋，通过吸收了秋所蕴含的所有色彩，落叶之焰也为龙的躯体染上了色彩。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Осенняя пора преобразила и чешую дракона, впитав в нее все краски осени и запечатлев на теле всполохи листопада.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
As escamas do dragão foram transformadas no puro Outono absorvendo as cores dele e refletindo as chamas das folhas caindo no corpo do dragão.

name: Ghost fire
description:
A skin for Cronus
This epic color earned in intense battles terrifies enemies and serves as a symbol of fighting merits. It's one of the rarest on Сronus.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
这个史诗般的颜色缘于激烈的战斗，能吓退敌人并且作为优秀战绩的象征。这是克罗努斯最罕见的成就之一。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Эпический окрас, заслуженный в тяжелых боях, нагоняет ужас на врагов и свидетельствует о признании боевых заслуг. Один из самых редких на кронусе.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
Essa cor épica adquirida em intensas batalhas aterroriza o inimigo e serve como um reconhecimento de méritos na batalha. É uma das mais raras em Cronus.

name: Hellfire
description:
A skin for Cronus
This epic color is won in the thick of the battle, in fire and chaos. Just the sight of it spreads bone-chilling terror among enemies.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
这个史诗般的颜色缘于在炮火和混乱交叠的战斗高峰中获胜。敌人一旦目睹了此便会毛骨悚然。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Эпический окрас, полученный в самом пекле битвы, среди огня и хаоса. Лишь один его вид наводит на врагов леденящий душу ужас.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
Essa cor épica é ganha na grossa batalha, no fogo e caos. Só olhar para ela reflete o terror sobre os inimigos.

name: Phantasm
description:
A skin for Cronus
The rarest color worthy of only the most skilled fighters who have survived deadly combat.
description_schinese:
克罗努斯（Cronus）的龙皮
最稀有的颜色，只为扭转了败局的高超战士加冕。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Кронус
Редчайший окрас, достойный лишь самых искусных бойцов, которые прошли испытание смертельным поединком.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Cronus
A Cor mais rara digna sómente dos mais habilidosos guerreiros que sobreviveram o combate mortal.

name: MSI Gaming skin
description: This skin can be obtained only by participating in MSI special events
description_schinese: This skin can be obtained only by participating in MSI special events
description_russian: Этот окрас может быть получен только участниками особых акций MSI
description_brazilian: This skin can be obtained only by participating in MSI special events

name: Cronus (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Cronus
description_schinese: 克罗努斯（Cronus）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Кронус
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Cronus

name: Ray (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Ray
description_schinese: 鳐鱼皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Скат
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Ray

name: Green combat color
description:
A skin for Ray
The scales of Rays that live in the marine reef acquire a greenish hue due to the coastal algae.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
鳐鱼生活在海洋的珊瑚礁附近，并且由于藻类的原因，其鳞片色调偏绿。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Скаты, обитающие у морских рифов, обретают зеленоватый оттенок чешуи благодаря прибрежным водорослям.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
As escamas dos Rays que vivem nos recifes marinhos adquiriram um tom verde azulado devido as algas

name: Blade
description:
A skin for Ray
Having gone through trial by fire under the blood-red moon, the Ray absorbed its rays and its scales started to look like rubies.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
在血月下经历了战斗的磨练，使鳐鱼的鳞片看起来像红宝石。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Пройдя боевое посвящение при кроваво-красной луне, скат впитал в себя ее лучи и чешуя его стала подобна рубинам.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Passando pelo desafio do fogo sobre a lua de sangue, o Ray absorveu seus raios e suas escamas começaram a parecer rubis

name: Tartu
description:
A skin for Ray
According to the ancient customs of secret assassins, Rays are garbed in dark colors so they can hover on the battlefield like shadows and stay inconspicuous.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
沿袭秘密暗杀者的古老传统，鳐鱼身着黑色，这使得他们能够像影子一样在战场上悬停，并且不易被发觉。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
По древним обычаям скрытных убийц, скатов обрекают в темные тона, благодаря которым они тенью мелькать на поле боя, оставаясь незамеченными.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Segundo os antigos costumes de assassinos secretos, Rays são envolvidos de cores negras, para voar sobre o campo de batalha e permanecerem imperceptiveis

name: Jade
description:
A skin for Ray
Dragons that look like sparkling stone sculptures live in the ruins of ancient jade palaces.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
那些鳞片闪闪发光的龙居住在古前朝的瑰丽宫殿的废墟中。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Нефритовые дворцы древних времен оставили от себя лишь руины, среди которых обитают драконы, более напоминающие изваяния из сверкающего камня.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Dragões que pareces cintilantes esculturas de pedras deixadas em antigos palácios Jades

name: Leopard
description:
A skin for Ray
Only the real killer is worthy of this color! Its look bears the features of a formidable predator making any enemy think twice before an attack!
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
只有真正的杀手才对得起这个颜色！他看上去是个很强大的捕食者，任何敌人看到他都会犹豫斟酌一下才敢进攻。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Лишь настоящий убийца достоин этого окраса! 
Облик его несет в себе черты грозного хищника и любой враг дважды подумает перед тем, как напасть на него!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Somente o real assassino é digno desta cor! Faz a função de fazer um predador formidável fazendo o inimigo pensar denovo antes de atacar

name: Pardus
description:
A skin for Ray
Like fleet footed predators Rays with this color are acknowledged to be the fastest and most maneuverable dragons on all Ahros.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
鳐鱼身着这个颜色，看起来就像是健步如飞的大鳄，是整个Ahros公认的速度最快和机动性最强的龙。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Подобно быстроногим хищникам, скаты, носящие этот окрас, признаются самыми быстрыми и маневренными драконами во всем Ахросе.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Como predadores acelerados Rays com essa cor são reconhecidos pelos mais velozes e melhores manobráveis dragões em toda Ahros

name: Midnight
description:
A skin for Ray
Midnight hunters are always quiet, but their outslandish color terrifies the enemies.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
午夜的猎者总是沉默默寡言的，但是其身上诡异的花纹让敌人感到恐怖。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Полночные охотники всегда тихи и незаметны, но облик их вызывает ужас своей диковинной окраской.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Caçadores da meia noite estão sempre quietos, mas a  sua cor estranha perturba os inimigos

name: Frost
description:
A skin for Ray
They say the Rays that live in the far north bear frost on their tails and look like blue ice under white snow.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
传言有一种在遥远的北方生活的鳐鱼，寒冻使他们的尾巴结冰，以至于他们看着就像是白雪覆盖着的蓝色冰凌。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Поговаривают, что скаты, обитающие на далеком севере, на своих хвостах несут морозные узоры, а облик их - синева льда под белоснежным снегом.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
É dito que os Rays que vivem no distante norte apresentam a nevasca em suas caldas e faz parecerem como o gelo azul debaixo da neve branca.

name: Insomnia
description:
A skin for Ray
The ancient Rays of Ahros acquired appearances worthy of their timeless merits. Their fading scales are covered with cracks, and on their wings is etched a redoubtable pair of all-seeing, eternally open eyes.
description_schinese:
鳐鱼的龙皮
The ancient Rays of Ahros acquired appearances worthy of their timeless merits. Their fading scales are covered with cracks, and on their wings is etched a redoubtable pair of all-seeing, eternally open eyes.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Скат
Древнейшие скаты Ахроса обретают облик, достойный их заслуг перед временем. Померкнувшая кожа покрывается трещинами, а на крыльях образуется внушающий уважения образ двух всевидящих, вечно открытых очей.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ray
Os antigos Rays de Ahros adquiriram a aparencia merecida de seus méritos incontáveis. Suas enfraquecidas escamas são cobertas com rachaduras, e uma imagem de dois olhos que já viram de tudo nas suas asas.

name: Ray (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Ray
description_schinese: 鳐鱼皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Скат
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Ray

name: Inara (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Inara
description_schinese: 伊纳拉（Inara）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Инара
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Inara

name: Green combat color
description:
A skin for Inara
Being stealthy on the battlefield is vital for any medic! That is why the natural grassy color is so popular among Inaras.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
对于任何一名医者，在战场隐身十分的重要，这就是为什么绿色保护色如此受欢迎。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Незаметность на поле боя - главный принцип любого медика! Именно поэтому природный, травянистый окрас так популярен среди Инар.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Ser sorrateiro no campo de batalha e um ponto chave para qualquer médico! Este é o motivo para a cor natural de grama ser tão popular em Inaras

name: Turquoise combat color
description:
A skin for Inara
A calm and serene turquoise glow bestows serenity for allies and sows suspicion in the ranks of the enemy.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
平和安详的绿松石的光芒，为战友带来平静，给敌人播下疑心的种子。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Спокойный и безмятежный отсвет бирюзы дарует спокойствие союзникам и сеет настороженность в ряды врагов.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Calma e serena Turquesa brilha e oferece serenidade para aliados e soa suspence ao nivel do inimigo

name: Red combat color
description:
A skin for Inara
 The most fierce healers of Ahros paint their Inaras in bright red color to show their intention to win at any cost.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
The most fierce healers of Ahros paint their Inaras in bright red color to show their intention to win at any cost.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Как бы подчеркивая свои намерения идти до победного конца любой ценой, особо ярые целительницы Ахроса окрашивают Инар в ярко-алый цвет.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Para enfatisar sua atenção até o fim à qualquer custo ardentes médicos de Ahros fizeram Inaras vermelho-brilhante

name: Smoldering ashes
description:
A skin for Inara
Inara tempered its body among the smoldering ruins and ashes of ancient battles by gaining the color that absorbed fading flames.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
伊纳拉在冒着硝烟的废墟和战场的灰烬中，磨砺了自己的躯体,得到了褪色火焰般的颜色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Среди тлеющих руин и пепелищ древних битв Инара закалила свое тело, приобретя окрас, который впитал в себя угасающее пламя.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Inara temperou seu corpo sobre as ruinas em combustão e cinzas sobre as antigas batalhas ganhando as cores absorvidas do fogo enfraquecido.

name: Granite
description:
A skin for Inara
Inaras living beside mines skillfully hid themselves among sandstone and granite rocks. Their scales looks like granite chips with sparkling whitish veins.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
伊纳拉能够巧妙地藏身于矿场附近的花岗岩和砂岩之中。他们的鳞片花纹看起来像是闪闪发光的花岗岩纹络。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Инары, обитающие у рудников, умело скрываются среди песчаника и гранитных скал. А их чешуя напоминает гранитную крошку, искрящуюся белесными прожилками.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Inaras vivendo dentre as minas habilidosamente se esconde sobre arenito e pedras de granito. Suas escamas parecem fichas de granito com suas cintilantes brancas veias

name: Green doctor
description:
A skin for Inara
Virtue and assistance can be hidden behind even the most fearsome and intimidating appearance.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
可怕狰狞的外表掩饰着高尚品德与奉献精神。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Даже самый грозный и устрашающий облик может скрывать за собой благодетель и помощь.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Virtude e assistencia podem se esconter até atraz da mais horripilante e intimidadora aparência.

name: White night
description:
A skin for Inara
Being stealthy in the night sky is the key to success. But even nights can be white and battles during such nights are faster than the light itself.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
Being stealthy in the night sky is the key to success. But even nights can be white and battles during such nights are faster than the light itself.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Скрытность в ночных небесах - залог успеха. Но даже ночи бывают белыми, а битвы в них - стремительнее самого света.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Ser sorrateiro no céu noturno é a chave para o sucesso. Porém inclusive as notes podem ser branca e batalhas nelas são mais rápidas que a própria luz

name: Wisps of chaos
description:
A skin for Inara
Wisps of the chaos born in the underground depths of Ahros have created Inara's poisonous acid color.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
来自Ahros地下深处的硝烟赐予了伊纳拉浓郁的毒性和酸性般的颜色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Взметнувшись в подземных глубинах Ахроса, дуновение хаоса породило ядовито-кислотное обличие Инары.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
Com o caos nascido nas profundesas de Ahros foi criado a cor de ácido venenoso da Inara

name: Shreds of the sun
description:
A skin for Inara
The sun leaves its mark everywhere... Its fiery flashes are seen even on the snow-white scales of the dragon.
description_schinese:
伊纳拉（Inara）的龙皮
太阳的光芒无处不及，那耀眼灼目的光芒即使在雪白的龙鳞上也能够闪烁着光彩。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Инара
Солнце везде оставляет свой след... и даже на белоснежной чешуе видны его огненные всполохи.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Inara
O sol deixa suas marcas em todo lugar... Suas marcas ardentes são vistas até nas escamas branco-neve deste dragão.

name: Inara (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Inara
description_schinese: 伊纳拉（Inara）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Инара
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Inara

name: Toxor (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Toxor
description_schinese: 脱火尔（Toxor）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Ядор
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Toxor

name: Cerberus
description:
A skin for Toxor
No wonder the color of this dragon is associated with poison, acidity, and death. Vapors of green poisons are particularly toxic. Anyone who breathes it in is doomed to a slow, agonizing death.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）的龙皮
难怪这条龙身上的颜色让人想到毒、硫酸和死亡。蒸发的绿色毒液有剧毒，任何龙吸入该气体都会注定缓慢的走向死亡。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Цвет этого дракона ассоциируется с ядом, кислотой, смертью. И не зря! Ведь испарения зеленых ядоров особо токсичны. Любой, кто их вдохнет, обречен на медленную смерть.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Sem duvidas a cor deste dragão está associada a envenenamento, ácido, morte. Evaporação de venenos verdes é particularmente tóxico. Qualquer um que respirar isto está condenado à morte

name: Skinless
description:
A skin for Toxor
Dragons marked with the color red have been famous for their aggressive attitudes for a long time. That's why the owners of Toxors whose scales have a red tint are renowned for their fierce tempers.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
一直以来，红颜色的龙因为好战的态度而闻名。因此，红色调脱火尔的所有者同样以好战暴躁的脾气闻名于世。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Помеченные красным цветом драконы издавна славились своим агрессивным настроем. Именно потому владельцы ядора, чья чешуя имеет красный оттенок, славятся своим яростным нравом.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Dragões marcados com a cor vermelha são famosos por sua agressíva atitude por um longo tempo. Por isso os donos de Toxors nas quais escamas tem uma tintura vermelha renunciaram por seu temperamento feroz.

name: Ninja
description:
A skin for Toxor
This color belongs to Toxors who are famous for their tactical and dangerous character. Black color symbolizes secrecy and causes  mystical fear …
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
这是一个代表有谋略之才和阴险属性的脱火尔的颜色。黑色象征着秘密和他人对未知事物的恐惧。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Расчетливым и опасным темпераментом отличаются ядоры, владеющие подобным окрасом, ведь черный цвет символизируют скрытность и таинственность. Черный цвет навеевает мистический страх..
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Essa cor pertence aos Toxors que são famozo por seus caráter tático e perigoso. A cor negra simboliza o sigilo e causa um medo místico.

name: Oxidation
description:
A skin for Toxor
Under long exposure to poisons and vapors, the scales of old Toxors become oxidized and a hard reddish coating appears on them.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
长期接触毒与水蒸气，年龄大的脱火尔的鳞片被氧化，身上形成了一个微红色的硬壳。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Под длительным воздействием ядов и испарений чешуя старых ядоров окисляется и на ней появляется жесткий налет красноватого цвета.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Depois de alta exposição à venenos e vapores, as escamas dos velhos Toxors viram oxidadas e uma camada vermelha aparece neles.

name: Realgar
description:
A skin for Toxor
Toxors that prefer distant and secretive lives in caves and abandoned mines are covered by a layer of rock dust which forms mineral coating on their scales.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
喜欢在遥远的洞穴和废弃山矿中过着神秘的生活的脱火尔，他们的鳞片被岩石粉尘形成的矿物外壳所覆盖。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Ядоры, предпочитающие отдаленную и скрытную жизнь в пещерах и заброшенных шахтах покрываются слоем горной пыли, которая образует на их чешуе минеральный налет.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Toxors que preferem distância e vida secreta nas cavernas e minas abandonadas foram cobertos por uma camada de pó de pedra que forma um manto mineram em suas escamas

name: Equilibrium
description:
A skin for Toxor
Do you know why Toxors are feared so much? Their deadly gas is not the only cause. Excellent balancing in the air and unprecedented mobility are things that terrify everyone.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
你知道为什么脱火尔如此骇人吗？他们能够致死的气体并不是唯一原因，他们在空气中极好的平衡性和前所未有的流动性也是让大家恐惧的原因。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Знаете ли вы, почему ядоров так опасаются? Не только смертоносный газ тому причиной служит. Идеальное равновесие в воздухе и небывалая маневренность - вот то, чего страшатся все.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Sabe por que Toxors são temidos? Seu gás mortal não é a única causa. Balanceamento aéreo e mobilidade sem precedentes assustam qualquer um.

name: Ergo
description:
A skin for Toxor
A huge number of marks on a Toxor’s body and coarsened skin are the distinctive marks of a real commander. Anyone who straddles such a dragon will be able to fight under any conditions!
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
脱火尔身体上大量的痕迹和粗糙的皮肤是一个将真正指挥官与其他龙区别开来的标志。如果能够骑这样的一条龙，那么他将在战场上无所畏惧！
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Огромное количество пометок на теле ядора и загрубевшая шкура  - знак отличия настоящего военнокомандующего! Тот, кто оседлал подобного дракона, сумеет вести бой в любых условиях!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Um grande número de marcas no corpo do Toxor e a aspereza da pele são marcas distintas de um verdadeiro comandante. Qualquer um que abrange este dragão poderá lutar em qualquer condição!

name: Remnants of the elements
description:
A skin for Toxor
Only those who survived raging fires and ocean storms, stayed alive after deadly battles are worthy of owning this dragon!
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
只有那些在战场上经受过烈火和海洋的灾难风暴并成功幸存、在致命的争斗后仍然活着的人才配享有这条龙！
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
Лишь прошедшие сквозь пламя и бури, выжившие в штормах среди океанов, уцелевшие в смертельных битвах достойны владеть этим драконом!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Somente aqueles que sobreviveram o fogo e as tempestades do oceano, ficaram vivos sobre as batalhas mortais são dignos de possuir este dragão!

name: Friable
description:
A skin for Toxor
Toxors are born in springs of mud volcanoes bubbling with poisonous gases . Their bodies are covered with a layer of rock and their poison is saturated with sulfur and methane.
description_schinese:
脱火尔（Toxor）
脱火尔出生于泥火山与有毒气体混合的冒泡泉水中。他们的身体覆盖有自身毒素、硫酸和甲烷饱和生成的硬壳。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Ядор
В бурлящих ядовитыми газами источниках грязевых вулканов рождаются ядоры, чье тело покрыто слоем горной породы, а яд их перенасыщен серой и метаном.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Toxor
Toxors nascem nas entranhas de vulcões barrosos eclodindo com gáses tóxicos. Seu corpo é coberto com uma camada de rochas e seu veneno é saturado com enxofre e metano.

description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Ядор

name: Ogre (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Ogre
description_schinese: 欧戈勒（Ogre）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Огр
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Ogro

name: Kid
description:
A skin for Ogre
Just the sight of this giant dragon colored by the night on the battlefield makes everyone tremble with terror.
That is why the ogres prefer dark colors.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Just the sight of this giant dragon colored by the night on the battlefield makes everyone tremble with terror.
That is why the ogres prefer dark colors.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Увидев на поле боя гигантского дракона цвета ночи, любой испытает страх перед ним. 
Именно поэтому огры предпочитают темную окраску.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Só o olhar deste dragão gigante colorido pela noite no campo de batalha faz todo mundo tremer de terror. É por isso que os Ogres preferem cores escuras.

name: Ferocious
description:
A skin for Ogre
Flickering with these colors in combat is like waving a red rag in front of the nose of the bull.
But opponents, who fall for this trick, have no idea what will happen next...
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Flickering with these colors in combat is like waving a red rag in front of the nose of the bull.
But opponents, who fall for this trick, have no idea what will happen next...
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Мелькать подобным окрасом в бою - все равно что махать красной тряпкой перед носом у быка. 
Но противники, попавшиеся на этот трюк, еще не знают, что их ждет...
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Ondular com essas cores no combate é como ter um pano vermelho na frente de um nariz de touro. Mas os oponentes, que são fisgados neste truque, não tem idéia do que acontece.

name: Veridan
description:
A skin for Ogre
Long-term exposure to the humid tropical jungle environment affected the skin of ogre. Bacteria and microorganisms that rapidly breed in such conditions gave a greenish tinge to the dragon's scales.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Long-term exposure to the humid tropical jungle environment affected the skin of ogre. Bacteria and microorganisms that rapidly breed in such conditions gave a greenish tinge to the dragon's scales.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Долгое пребывание во влажных тропических джунглях повлияло на кожу огра. Бактерии и микроорганизмы, быстро развивающиеся в таких условиях, придали зеленоватый оттенок чешуе дракона.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Exposição a longo praso para a mata úmida afetou a pele do Ogre. Bactérias e microorganismos que rapidamente nasceram em tais condições deram este tom esverdiado às escamas do dragão.

name: Ultraviolet
description:
A skin for Ogre
Barely visible spots of violet color appeared on the dark scales of Ogre due the impact of laser and ultraviolet radiation.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Barely visible spots of violet color appeared on the dark scales of Ogre due the impact of laser and ultraviolet radiation.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Едва заметные пятна фиолетового цвета появились на темной чешуе огра из-за воздействия на дракона лазерного и ультрафиолетового излучения.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Manchas dificilmente visiveis da cor violeta apareceram nas escamas do Ogro pelo impacto de laser e de radiação ultra-violeta.

name: Golem
description:
A skin for Ogre
No wonder that a huge powerful dragon, whose body is covered with a layer of hardened clay, is called Golem. Like a clay giant, he has outstanding strength and endurance.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
No wonder that a huge powerful dragon, whose body is covered with a layer of hardened clay, is called Golem. Like a clay giant, he has outstanding strength and endurance.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Огромный мощный дракон, тело которого покрыто слоем застывшей глины, недаром зовется Големом. Подобно глиняным великанам, он обладает  недюжинной силой и выносливостью.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Sem dúvidas que um grande e poderoso dragão, no qual o corpo está coberto com argila endurecida, é chamado de Golem. Como um gigante de argina, possui força incomum e resistencia espantosa.

name: Ghost
description:
A skin for Ogre
From a distance, Ogre seems to be covered with intricate characters that resemble a skeleton shrouded in darkness. Perhaps this is why dragons with such coloring is often called ghosts.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
From a distance, Ogre seems to be covered with intricate characters that resemble a skeleton shrouded in darkness. Perhaps this is why dragons with such coloring is often called ghosts.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Покрытая затейливыми знаками чешуя огра издали напоминает скелет, окутанный тьмой. Возможно поэтому драконов с таким окрасом зачастую называют призраками.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Ao distante, o Ogre parece estar coberto com detalhadas figuras que formam um esqueleto coberto pela escuridão. Talvez por este motivo dragões com essa coloração são chamados Fantasmas.

name: Camouflage
description:
A skin for Ogre
Camouflage coloring of this Ogre helps it to adapt to any terrain and attack the enemy while being unspotted.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Camouflage coloring of this Ogre helps it to adapt to any terrain and attack the enemy while being unspotted.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Камуфляжный окрас этого огра помогает ему приспосабливаться к любой местности и незаметно вести обстрел противника по всем фронтам.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
O coloramento camuflado deste Ogro ajuda-o à se adaptar à qualquer terreno e o ajuda à atacar o inimigo sem nem mesmo ser visto

name: Butterfly
description:
A skin for Ogre
Seeing an Ogre with this coloring makes you think of butterflies. Huge and deadly butterflies.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Seeing an Ogre with this coloring makes you think of butterflies. Huge and deadly butterflies.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Встретив на поле боя огра с подобной окраской, любой невольно поймает себя на мысли, что видит перед собою бабочку. Огромную и смертоносную бабочку.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Ver um ogro com esta coloração faz você pensar em borboletas. Grandes e mortais borboletas.

name: Savage
description:
A skin for Ogre
Berserkers, who live in the plains, bred this kind of ogres, famous for wild temper and strength. Their scarlet skin is covered with multiple wounds and scratches that they got in numerous battles.
description_schinese:
欧戈勒（Ogre）的龙皮
Berserkers, who live in the plains, bred this kind of ogres, famous for wild temper and strength. Their scarlet skin is covered with multiple wounds and scratches that they got in numerous battles.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Огр
Берсерки, живущие на равнинах, вывели вид огров, славящихся диким нравом и силой. Алая кожа их покрыта множеством ран и царапин, полученных в битвах.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Ogro
Brutamontes, que vivem nas planices, criaram esse tipo de Ogre, famoso pelo seu comportamento selvagem e força. Sua pele escarlante é coberta por diversas feridas e riscos que eles ganharam em diferentes batalhas.

description: Full set of skins for Tiamat
description_schinese: 提阿马特（Tiamat）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Тиамат
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Tiamat

name: Green combat color
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Deceptively peaceful green color of Tiamat was specially designed to confuse enemies and win time to attack them.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
专为提亚马特设计的绿色，看似无害，能够迷惑敌人和争取时间发出攻击。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Обманчиво-мирный зеленый окрас Тиамата на то и рассчитан, чтобы сбивать с толку врага и атаковать, пока он не опомнится.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
A ilusória pacífica cor verde do Tiamat foi designata especificamente para confundir o inimigo e ganhar tempo para os atacar.

name: Red combat color
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Red is the color of threat and danger. That's why it's probably chosen for combat coloring of adragons. Timat in scarlet color looks more intimidating than anyone else!
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
红色代表危险和威胁，这也是让红色作为其中一种战斗颜色的原因。猩红色的提亚马特比其他颜色看起来更有威慑力。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Красный цвет - цвет угрозы, цвет опасности. Возможно потому его выбирают для боевых раскрасок драконов. А Тиамат в алых тонах выглядит наиболее устрашающе, чем кто либо!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Vermelho é a cor do perigo e ameaça. Por isso é escolhida para coloração de combate para dragões. Timat em uma cor scarlate fica mais entimidador que qualquer outro!

name: Blue combat color
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Is it the color of the sky or deep sea? Your opponents will have to answer this question on the battlefield... If they have time to say anything before their death.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
这个难道不是天空和深海的颜色吗？你的对手会在战场上回答这个问题，前提是他们临死之前还有时间开口说话。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Небесная синева или морская пучина? Ответ на этот вопрос дадут вам противники на поле брани...Если успеют сказать хоть что нибудь перед смертью.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
É a cor do céu ou do fundo do oceano? Seis oponentes terão que responder esta pergunta no campo de batalha... se tiverem tempo de dizer algo antes de falecerem.

name: Abyss
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Once Tiamat fell into the sea and the sea abyss swallowed it. The dragon has survived, but the sea salt ingrained in its scales and forever changed their color.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
一旦提亚马特掉进了海里，被吞噬入海的深渊，龙却幸存了下来，海水中的盐分溶进了龙的鳞片，永远的改变了龙鳞的颜色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Однажды Тиамат рухнул в море и бездна морская поглотила его. Дракон выжил, но морская соль въелась в чешую и навсегда изменила ее цвет.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Quando Tiamat caiu no oceano o abismo o digeriu. Mas o dragão sobreviveu, porém o sal preso nas suas escamas mudou para sempre suas cores.

name: Pagan
description:
A skin for Tiamat
There are legends that in the deaf Ahros jungles druid pagans tamed a special kind of Tiamats which carry the fury of the nature in their appearance to this day.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
There are legends that in the deaf Ahros jungles druid pagans tamed a special kind of Tiamats which carry the fury of the nature in their appearance to this day.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Ходят легенды, что в глухих Джунглях Ахроса друиды-язычники приручили особый вид Тиаматов, которые и по сей день несут в своем облике всю ярость природы.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Existem lendas que nas distantes selvas de Ahros pagões duidras criaram um tipo especial de Tiamats que carregam a fúria da natureza na sua aparência.

name: Sunset
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Illumined by the setting sun Tiamat absorbed the scorching rays of the sun and now carries the glow of sunset inside.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
在夕阳的光辉照耀下，提亚马特吸收了太阳灼热的光芒，并带着这光芒飞入太阳的中心。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Озаренный заходящим солнцем Тиамат впитал в себя палящие лучи, и отныне несет в себе зарево заката.
description_brazilian: Iluminado pelo sol poente Tiamat absorveu os escaldantes raios do sol e agora carrega consigo o brilho do pôr do sol.

name: Anubis
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Like an ancient god a dragon with this color escorts the dead to the afterlife. Or does it send them there?
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
Like an ancient god a dragon with this color escorts the dead to the afterlife. Or does it send them there?
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Подобно древнему божеству, носитель этого окраса является проводником мертвых в загробный мир..Или же, он сам их туда отправляет?
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Um antigo dragão com essas cores escorta a morte para a outra vida. Ou ele as manda lá? (This phrase doesn't make any sence at all)

name: Bloody God
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Sprinkled with blood of its enemies Tiamat will always possess a dark red color which demonstrates its ruthlessness.
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
血溅敌手，这样的暗红色，十分形象地彰显着提亚马特的残酷和冷血。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Окропленный кровью своих врагов, Тиамат навсегда приобрел темно-алый окрас, показывающий всю его беспощадность.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Salpicado com o sangue de seus inimigos Tiamat vai sempre possuir uma cor vermelho-escuro que demonstra sua crueldade.

name: Ra
description:
A skin for Tiamat
Noble gold and righteous rage! This is the true face of the strongest of Tiamats! To tame such a dragon is the highest merit of real experts!
description_schinese:
提阿马特（Tiamat）的龙皮
高贵的金色和正义之愤怒！这是最强提亚马特的真面目！能够驯服这样的龙是真正的战士至高的荣耀！
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Тиамат
Благородное золото и праведная ярость - вот истинный облик сильнейшего из Тиаматов! Приручить такого - высшая заслуга настоящих мастеров!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Tiamat
Nobre ouro e raiva justificada! Esta é a real face do mais forte dos Tiamats! Para domesticar um destes dragões é preciso o maior mérito dos reais especialistas.

description: Full set of skins for Tiamat
description_schinese: 提阿马特（Tiamat）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Тиамат
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Tiamat

name: Fury (Full set of skins)
description: Full set of skins for Fury
description_schinese: 夫里雅（Fury）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Фурия
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Fúria

name: Blue combat color
description:
A skin for Fury
Ahros heaven is not so calm and safe as it seems from Earth. After all, Furies with the color of the sky hover it freely.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
Ahros的天堂并不像从地球上看着的那么祥和。毕竟有着天空色的Furies在上空自由的徜徉。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Поднебесье Ахроса не так спокойно и безопасно, как кажется с земли. Ведь в нем парят Фурии, окрасом своим сливающиеся с небом.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
O céu de Ahros não é tão calmo e seguro como parece da Terra. Mesmo assim, Furies com esta cor planam sobre ele livremente.

name: Red combat color
description:
A skin for Fury
In order to intimidate opponents some Furies add a blood-red hue to their scales, which is noticeable from a distance and resembles dried blood.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
为了威慑对手，Furies在龙鳞上增添了血红色，从远处就能够被注意到，看起来就像干涸了的血液。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Для устрашения противников некоторые фурии придают своей чешуе кроваво-красный оттенок, заметный издали и напоминающий запекшуюся кровь.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Para intimidar os oponentes algumas Furies adicionam uma tonalidade vermelho-sangue para suas escamas, que é notável de longe e lembra sangue seco.

name: Green combat color
description:
A skin for Fury
Staying among extensive meadows and dense forests caused Fury to adapt and acquire a new coloring - the color of luscious greenery.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
在茂盛的草地和森林中，Furies为了适应环境，进化出了新的颜色——甘美的绿色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Пребывание среди обширных лугов и дремучих лесов заставило фурию приспосабливаться и обрести новую окраску - цвета сочной зелени.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Permanecendo sobre longos prados e densas florestas causou Fury a se adaptar e conseguir esta nova coloração - um exuberante verde.

name: Desert viper
description:
A skin for Fury
This unusual color is acquired in long battles to protect the desert borders of the empire.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
为了保卫帝国，长期在帝国的沙漠边缘战斗，久而久之就形成了这个特殊的颜色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Необыкновенный окрас, приобретенный в продолжительных боях на защите пустынных рубежей империи.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Esta cor incomum é adquirida nas longas batalhas para proteger as bordas desérticas do império.

name: Red horror
description:
A skin for Fury
This is the place where fire replaces plants and water is replaced by lava. This is the place where Furies with the color terrifying any enemy are born.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
曾经火焰吞噬了这里植物与水，最终又被熔岩所取代。是具有威慑色的Furies的出生地。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Место, где огонь заменяет растения. Место, где вместо воды - лава. Это место, где рождаются Фурии с окрасом, наводящим ужас на всякого врага.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Este é o lugar onde o fogo substitui plantas e lava substitui água. Este é o lugar onde espantosos Furies nascem.

name: Ice viper
description:
A skin for Fury
This unusual color is gained in the battles among snowy plains, a place where there are only storms and blizzards and time has frozen in the cold clasp. And only a battle-hardened dragon can survive here.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
这个特殊的颜色是在一个只有暴风雨雪、时间也被冻住的冰天雪地环境下战斗磨砺出来的。只有唯一的胜者才能在这里生存下去。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Необыкновенный окрас, приобретенный в битвах среди снежных равнин - месте, где лишь бури и вьюги, а время замерзает в объятиях холода. И лишь закаленный боями дракон сможет выжить здесь.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Esta cor incomum é ganha nas batalhas sobre as planices geladas, um lugar onde existe somente tempestades e nevascas e o tempo congelou no aperto do frio. Somente um dragão enrijecido pela guerra conseguiria sobreviver lá.

name: Fiery cobra
description:
A skin for Fury
No one can stop the violent attack of a cobra! It has enough power to stop and destroy hordes of enemies.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
没有人能够抵挡眼镜蛇的猛烈攻击！它很强大，足以抵挡和消灭掉成群的敌人。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Никто не сможет остановить яростную атаку кобры! Уж с ней то у вас хватит сил  для того, чтобы остановить и уничтожить орды неприятеля.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Ninguém poderia parar o ataque de uma naja! Ela tem poder suficiente para destruir hordas de inimigos!

name: Vendetta
description:
A skin for Fury
The combination of simple and complex, rage and serenity. Your opponent will be stunned by your achievement. This color is not easy to earn! It is a sign of the highest degree of excellence and your skills to fight with this dragon.
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
这是简洁与繁琐、愤怒与静谧的结合。你的对手会被你所取得的成就威慑到。这个颜色很难得到。与这条龙战斗，彰显着你高超过人的天赋与技巧。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Сочетание простого и сложного, ярости и спокойствия. Ваш противник будет ошеломлен вашим достижением. Этот окрас заработать совсем не просто! Наивысшая степень совершенства и мастерства управления данным драконом.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
A Combinação de simples e complexo, raiva e serenidade. Seu oponente vai ficar espantado por sua conquista. Esta cor não é simples de alcançar! É uma prova do maior grau de excelência e suas habilidades com este dragão.

name: Valour
description:
A skin for Fury
Valor and Honor! This is the motto of the dragon with this color. This is the motto of the one who was able to tame it and to fight on top of it!
description_schinese:
夫里雅（Fury）的龙皮
勇气和荣耀！——是这个颜色所蕴含的真理。是为能够驯服它并能够在其背上战斗之人而诞生的铭牌。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Фурия
Доблесть и честь! Вот девиз дракона, носящего данный окрас. Вот девиз того, кто смог приручить и сражаться верхом на нем!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Fúria
Valor e honra! Este é o lema do dragão com esta cor. Este é o dilema de quem foi hábil para domar e lutar com este dragão!

description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Фурия

description: Full set of skins for Vampire
description_schinese: 吸血鬼（Vampire）皮肤全定义
description_russian: Полный набор окрасов для дракона Вампир
description_brazilian: Set completo de peles para Vampiro

name: Black combat color
description:
A skin for Vampire
The heat of volcanic fumes makes the scales of dragons flying near them smolder and melt. After stiffening their scales take on a new black shade.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
火山烟尘的热量使龙的鳞片融化重塑。经过磨炼后，他们的鳞片呈现出黑色的阴影。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Жар вулканических испарений заставляет чешую пролетающих мимо драконов тлеть и плавиться. Застывая же, чешуя приобретает новый, черный оттенок.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
O calor da fumaça vulcânica faz as escamas dos dragões próximos entrar em combustão e derreter. Após endurecer, suas escamas ganham uma nova tonalidade negra.

name: Red combat color
description:
A skin for Vampire
Vampires feed themselves with the blood of their enemies. When there is too much blood, it washes their bodies dying the scales a rich scarlet color.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
吸血鬼龙靠敌人的血液来喂养自己，当血液超过他们的需求时，他们会用多余的血液来清洗鳞片，于是鳞片便呈现出一种鲜艳的殷红色。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Вампиры насыщаются кровью своих врагов, а когда крови слишком много - она омывает их тела, создавая насыщенный алый цвет.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Vampires se alimentam com o sangue fresco de seus inimigos. Quando tem muito sangue, ele lava seus corpos tingindo seus corpos com uma rica cor escarlate.

name: Green combat color
description:
A skin for Vampire
Green plains, now withered and faded, used to be the habitat of Vampires with a bright green color which are now much more difficult to meet.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
以往的绿色平原，现已枯萎褪色。这里曾经是吸血鬼龙生机勃勃的绿色栖息地，而现在很难再找到这样的地方了。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Зеленые равнины, ныне высохшие и увядшие, были местом обитания Вампиров с ярко-зеленой окраской, которых сейчас встретить гораздо сложнее.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Planices verdes, agora murchas e apagadas, eram as moradias de Vampires com uma brilhante cor verde que agora são difíceis de se encontrar.

name: The beginning of the fire
description:
A skin for Vampire
Long ago Vampires carried sparks of flame inside them. But the fire was consumed over the centuries leaving a memory in the form of patterns on the body of some dragons.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
Long ago Vampires carried sparks of flame inside them. But the fire was consumed over the centuries leaving a memory in the form of patterns on the body of some dragons.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Давным-давно Вампиры имели в себе искры пламени. Но с веками огонь истлел, оставив память о себе в виде узоров на теле  некоторых драконов.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Muito tempo atrás, Vampiros carregavam faíscas de fogo dentro deles. Porém o fogo foi consumido durante os séculos deixando uma memória na forma de padrões no corpo de alguns dragões.

name: Daredevil
description:
A skin for Vampire
Agitated by bloody battles Vampires often lose their vigilance and receive wounds and injuries that are imprinted on their bodies in bold patterns.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
Agitated by bloody battles Vampires often lose their vigilance and receive wounds and injuries that are imprinted on their bodies in bold patterns.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Взбудораженные кровопролитными битвами Вампиры зачастую теряют бдительность, получая раны и увечья,  которые дерзкими узорами отпечатываются на их теле.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Agitado por sanguentas batalhas, Vampires perdem sua concentração e recebem machucados que são cravados neles com padrões negritos.

name: Taking to the afterworld
description:
A skin for Vampire
No wonder this Vampire has such a name. Its ruthlessness in battles and desire to win claimed hundreds of lives.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
No wonder this Vampire has such a name. Its ruthlessness in battles and desire to win claimed hundreds of lives.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Не зря такое название у этого Вампира.  
Его беспощадность в битвах и ярое стремление победить унесло сотни жизней в мир иной.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Sem dúvida este Vampire tem um belo nome. Sua crueldade nas batalhas e seu desejo pela vitória tomou centenas de vidas.

name: A lethal whiff
description:
A skin for Vampire
Vampires are born in dark caves among the massive cliffs and deep canyons. Their mission is to shed blood and bring death to the enemy in a swift cloud of chaos.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
Vampires are born in dark caves among the massive cliffs and deep canyons. Their mission is to shed blood and bring death to the enemy in a swift cloud of chaos.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Среди массивных скал и в глубоких ущельях, во тьме пещерных сводов рождаются вампиры, чье призвание - проливать кровь и убивать, стремительным облаком хаоса неся смерть врагам.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Vampires que nascem em escuras cavernas sobre os enormes penhascos e profundos abismos. Sua missão é derramar sangue e trazer a morte para o inimigo em uma rápida nuvem de caos.

name: Predator
description:
A skin for Vampire
Harsh living conditions among the rocks and desert turned these dragons into real predators. Adaptability to the environment gave them a characteristic color.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
Harsh living conditions among the rocks and desert turned these dragons into real predators. Adaptability to the environment gave them a characteristic color.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Суровые условия проживания среди скал и пустынных дюн воспитали в этом драконе нрав настоящего хищника. А приспособляемость к окружающей среде одарила его характерной окраской.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Difíceis condições de vidas sobre pedras e desertos transformou estes dragões em reais predadores. Sere, adaptáveis ào ambiente lhes proporcionou uma cor característica.

name: Apache
description:
A skin for Vampire
There is an ancient ritual among ancient triebs to render the bloody sacrifice to the vampire-dragon and then mark its scales with hieroglyphs of their family line.
description_schinese:
吸血鬼（Vampire）的龙皮
这是一个流传于古老种族的古老仪式，将鲜血浸染到吸血鬼龙的身上，在鳞片上呈现出他们的家族特有的图腾。
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Вампир
Среди диких племен существует древний ритуал - воздавать кровавую жертву дракону-вампиру, а потом помечать его шкуру письменами-иероглифами своего рода.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Vampiro
Existe um antigo ritual sobre tribos antigas para dedicar o ritual de sangue para o dragão vampiro e então marcar suas escamas com hieróglifos de sua linha familiar.

name: Azure combat color
description:
A skin for Hyperion
Azure skies is a favorite place of dragons that appreciate freedom.
Color merging with the sky is a perfect disguise.
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Лазурные небеса - излюбленное место драконов, ценящих свободу и простор. 
А окрас, сливающийся с небом - отличная маскировка.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Hyperion
Os céis azulados são o lugar preferido dos dragões que apreciam a liberdade. A cor se fundindo com o céu é uma camuflagem perfeita.

name: Ochre
description:
A skin for Hyperion
Dragons whose habitat is desert mines acquire a reddish color of scales. Oxidized metal and the abundance of clay influence dragon bodies, changing their color.
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Драконы, чье место обитания - пустынные рудники, приобретают рыжеватый цвет чешуи. Окисленные металлы и обилие глины в тех местах влияют и на тела драконов, меняя их цвет
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Hyperion
Dragões de qual o hábitat são desertos e minas ganha escamas avermelhadas. Metal oxidado e a abundância de argila influenciaram no corpo destes dragões, mudando suas cores.

name: Cardinal
description:
A skin for Hyperion
From the beginning of times crimson color symbolized power and strength. Or blood and death ...
That's why the ones who choose red tones for coloring are considered dangerous opponents!
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Алый цвет издревле символизирует власть и силу! Или же кровь и смерть…
Именно потому те, кто выбирает красные тона для окрасов, считаются опасными противниками!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Hyperion
A partir do começo dos tempos a cor púrpura simboliza poder e força. Ou sangue e morte ... Por isto quem prefere tons vermelhos são considerados oponentes letais!

name: Granite crumb
description:
A skin for Hyperion
Grayish scales of the dragon are covered with dark streaks that curl all over the body. Only highland dragons have this type of coloring.
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Сероватая чешуя этих драконов испещрена темными прожилками, которые вьются по всему телу. Подобная окраска есть лишь у обитателей горных вершин.
description_brazilian: Uma pele para Hyperion

name: Magma splash
description:
A skin for Hyperion
The body of the dragon absorbed raging flames of the battle. Magma flows in its veins, giving the rage and heat for new victories!
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Жилы этого дракона впитали в себя бурлящее пламя битвы. Магма течет в его венах, раскаляя тело и давая ярости и жара для новых побед!
description_brazilian: Uma pele para Hyperion

name: Aggressor
description:
A skin for Hyperion
An ardent, aggressive and bright color draws attention due to its contrast, annoying and enraging enemies, causing their hastening and mistakes. And while you are in combat mistakes come with a very high price...
description_schinese: 亥伯龙的龙皮
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Гиперион
Ярый, агрессивный и яркий окрас привлекает своим контрастом, раздражает противников и злит их, заставляя спешить и делать ошибки. А ошибки в бою обходятся очень дорого...
description_brazilian: Uma pele para Hyperion

name: Jade hammer
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
Ancient jade palaces left behind nothing but ruins, which are inhabited by rays that resemble sculptures of sparkling mineral.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
Ancient jade palaces left behind nothing but ruins, which are inhabited by rays that resemble sculptures of sparkling mineral.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Древние нефритовые дворцы оставили от себя одни только руины, в которых водятся скаты,напоминающие изваяния из сверкающего минерала.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
Ancient jade palaces left behind nothing but ruins, which are inhabited by rays that resemble sculptures of sparkling mineral.

name: Granite hammer
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
In the dark dungeons of granite, near the bubbling deep rivers leaves a tribe of demons, whose skin is made of stone, and their weapons are lightning bolts.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
In the dark dungeons of granite, near the bubbling deep rivers leaves a tribe of demons, whose skin is made of stone, and their weapons are lightning bolts.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Во тьме гранитных подземелий, рядом с бурлящими глубинными реками обитают демоны, чья шкура - камень, а оружие - разряды молний.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
In the dark dungeons of granite, near the bubbling deep rivers leaves a tribe of demons, whose skin is made of stone, and their weapons are lightning bolts.

name: Storm hammer
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
Devil Ray, born in the heart of a violent storm, is like a storm elemental. Blasts of thunder and flashes of lightning - this is his natural habitat!
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
Devil Ray, born in the heart of a violent storm, is like a storm elemental. Blasts of thunder and flashes of lightning - this is his natural habitat!
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Демонический скат, рожденный в сердце яростной бури, подобен штормовому элементалю. Раскаты грома и всполохи молний - вот его стихия!
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
Devil Ray, born in the heart of a violent storm, is like a storm elemental. Blasts of thunder and flashes of lightning - this is his natural habitat!

name: Ash
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
Plains covered with volcanic ash are not as lifeless and deserted as it seems to a lone traveler at first glance.
An ash blown up by the wind reveals a gray ray that was disguised by it.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
Plains covered with volcanic ash are not as lifeless and deserted as it seems to a lone traveler at first glance.
An ash blown up by the wind reveals a gray ray that was disguised by it.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Равнины, осыпанные вулканическим пеплом, не так безжизненны и пустынны, как кажется на первый взгляд одинокому путнику. 
Всколыхнется в воздух пепел и явится серый скат, скрывавшийся ранее от чужих взглядов.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
Plains covered with volcanic ash are not as lifeless and deserted as it seems to a lone traveler at first glance.
An ash blown up by the wind reveals a gray ray that was disguised by it.

name: Venomous
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
Redoubtable bright skin confuses and scares away unwanted enemies.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
Redoubtable bright skin confuses and scares away unwanted enemies.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей
Устрашающая яркая расцветка отпугивает нежеланных противников и сбивает их с толку.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
Redoubtable bright skin confuses and scares away unwanted enemies.

name: Veteran
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
The most ancient Devil Rays of Ahros acquire appearance that emphasizes their age. Their skin hardens and acquires a metallic sheen, and their scales become as hard as stone.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
The most ancient Devil Rays of Ahros acquire appearance that emphasizes their age. Their skin hardens and acquires a metallic sheen, and their scales become as hard as stone.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Древнейшие демонические скаты Ахроса обретают облик, подчеркивающий их возраст. Их кожа застывает и обретает металлический блеск, а чешуя становится твердой, как камень.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
The most ancient Devil Rays of Ahros acquire appearance that emphasizes their age. Their skin hardens and acquires a metallic sheen, and their scales become as hard as stone.

name: Sun ray
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
The scales of Devil Rays burn out in the hot desert sun and gain a dark golden hue.
description_schinese:
蝠鲼的龙皮
The scales of Devil Rays burn out in the hot desert sun and gain a dark golden hue.
description_russian:
Окрас на дракона Девил Рей 
Чешуя демонических скатов выгорает в лучах раскаленного солнца пустыни и приобретает темно-золотистый оттенок.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Devil ray
The scales of Devil Rays burn out in the hot desert sun and gain a dark golden hue.

name: Anger
description:
A skin for Devil Ray
Features of a formidable predator in combination with a demonic appearance of the Devil Ray create a truly terrible image, and make you understand that messing with this dragon is a bad idea.

Дракон, попавший в отравленные кислотами облака, не сможет более похвастаться сверкающей чешуей. А тело его будет разъедено парами и ядами. Такова цена кислотного шторма.
description_brazilian:
Uma pele para Rage
The dragon caught in the poisoned acid cloud can no longer boast of shiny scales. Its body will be corroded with gases and poisons. This is the price of being caught in the acid storm.
